anana''\n| \n|  \n|\n|<ref name=galactic/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: Blarpo''\n| \n| Blarpo\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: Briny''\n| \n|  Briny En Garde! (Terry Cooke) (UK)\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: Dangerous Liaisons''\n| \n| Jerry Spencer\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: Delon''\n| \n| Richard Crofts\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: Horseguards''\n| \n| Trevor Gillard\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: King & Cardinal''\n| \n| Ian Coleman (UK)\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: LPBS''\n| \n| Paul Evans (UK)\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: Orc''\n| \n| Aramaro Adrian\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: Orleans''\n| \n|  \n|\n|<ref name=galactic/> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: Slumbers''\n| \n| Brian Jenkins\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: Star''\n| \n| Pete Cooney\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''EG!: Time of Honor''\n| \n| Quincy Cooper\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Einstein's Lot''\n| \n| Ulaidh Games (Ireland, UK)\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Eldritch''\n| \n| Play-by-Electron Games\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Election Year''\n| \n| [[Flying Buffalo Inc]]\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/>, <ref>{{cite magazine |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |title= PBM Activity Corner|url= |magazine= [[Paper Mayhem]]|location= |publisher= The Paper Mayhem Association |issue= 67|page= 35|date= July\u2013August 1994|access-date= }}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''El Mythico''\n|\n|[[Graaf Simulations]]\n|\n|<ref name=\"mayhem ratings jan 95\"/>, <ref name=galactic/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Empires''\n| \n| Software Simulations (UK)\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/> \n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Empires of Corinium''\n| \n| Viking Games\n|\n|<ref name=galactic/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | 