|date=2016-11-03}}</ref>\n|\n|-\n| 2019\n| ''[[The Outpost (2019 film)|The Outpost]]''\n| 1st Lieutenant Benjamin D. Keating\n| Post-production\n|-\n| TBA\n| ''[[Needle in a Timestack]]''\n| \n| Post-production\n|}\n\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 1994\u201396\n| ''[[Casualty (TV series)|Casualty]]''\n| Noel Harrison\n| Episodes: \"Care in the Community\", \"Another Day in Paradise\", \"Made in Britain\"\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[Midsomer Murders]]''\n| Peter Drinkwater\n| Episode: \"Judgement Day\"\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[Extras (TV series)|Extras]]''\n| Himself\n| Episode: \"Orlando Bloom\"\n|-\n|2011\n| ''[[Los Angeles Philharmonic|LA Phil Live]]''\n| Romeo\n| Episode: \"Dudamel Conducts Tchaikovsky\"\n|-\n| 2016\n| ''[[Easy (TV series)|Easy]]''\n| Tom \n| Episode: \"Utopia\"\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2017\n| ''[[Tour de Pharmacy]]''\n| Juju Peppi\n| Television film\n|-\n| ''[[Stairway to Stardom]]''\n| Himself\n| 1 episode\n|-\n| 2019\u2013present\n| ''[[Carnival Row]]''\n| Rycroft Philostrate\n| <ref>{{cite web|last1=Andreeva|first1=Nellie|title=Orlando Bloom To Star In 'Carnival Row' Fantasy Drama Series For Amazon|url=http://deadline.com/2017/08/orlando-bloom-cast-carnival-row-amazon-fantasy-drama-series-1202156081/|website=Deadline Hollywood|accessdate=15 December 2017|date=25 August 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216091413/http://deadline.com/2017/08/orlando-bloom-cast-carnival-row-amazon-fantasy-drama-series-1202156081/|archive-date=16 December 2017|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|}\n\n===Video games===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Voice role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2002\n| ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers (video game)|The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers]]''\n| rowspan=\"6\" | Legolas\n| rowspan=\"7\" | Archive sound\n|-\n| 2003\n| ''[[The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King (video game)|The Lord of the Rings: Th